  'title': "WHO warns of 'biological risk' after Sudan fighters seize lab, as violence mars US-brokered ceasefire - CNN",
  'summary': "The World Health Organization warns of a 'huge biological risk' after Sudanese fighters seize the National Public Health Laboratory in Khartoum amidst ongoing violence. A fragile ceasefire has been punctured by continued fighting, and at least 459 people have been killed with over 4,000 injured. Foreign nations are racing to evacuate their citizens as the situation worsens.",
